

{"id":4411,"date":"2023-06-13T14:32:09","date_gmt":"2023-06-13T07:32:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tnt.locdt.site\/staging\/?p=4411"},"modified":"2023-08-29T13:04:16","modified_gmt":"2023-08-29T06:04:16","slug":"vi-sao-chung-can","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/vi-sao-chung-can\/","title":{"rendered":"V\u00ec sao b\u1ea1n b\u1ecb ch\u1eefng c\u00e2n?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Ch\u1eefng c\u00e2n<\/strong>? Ch\u1eefng c\u00e2n l\u00e0 g\u00ec? V\u00ec sao b\u1ecb ch\u1eefng c\u00e2n?\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ch\u1eefng c\u00e2n l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi l\u00fac m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp. V\u1eady l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c ch\u1eefng c\u00e2n?<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><br \/>\n2 l\u00fd do b\u1ea1n b\u1ecb ch\u1eefng c\u00e2n:<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">1\/ C\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4983 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/tap-bung-co-lam-giam-mo-bung.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/tap-bung-co-lam-giam-mo-bung.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/tap-bung-co-lam-giam-mo-bung-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/tap-bung-co-lam-giam-mo-bung-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/tap-bung-co-lam-giam-mo-bung-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/tap-bung-co-lam-giam-mo-bung-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn \u0111ang s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ee9c t\u1ea1 v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 set t\u1eadp t\u1eeb l\u00fac m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp, ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea1y v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u00ean m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9? B\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 b\u00e0i t\u1eadp b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 g\u00ec, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean b\u00e0i t\u1eadp v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 trong v\u00f2ng v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. C\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta th\u00edch nghi r\u1ea5t nhanh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c gi\u00e1o \u00e1n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n n\u00ean n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f3 t\u0103ng d\u1ea7n, th\u00ec c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f3 3 c\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cho c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp:<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u0103ng m\u1ee9c t\u1ea1 m\u00ecnh n\u00e2ng: B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u0103ng m\u1ee9c t\u1ea1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean s\u1ed1 set t\u1eadp. \u1ede ph\u00f2ng gym c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u0129a t\u1ea1 t\u1eeb 0.25kg t\u1edbi 1kg \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00eam v\u00e0o cho c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n t\u0103ng m\u1ee9c t\u1ea1 qu\u00e1 nhanh, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn k\u0129 thu\u1eadt l\u00fac t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 theo sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng cao. N\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u0103ng s\u1ed1 rep t\u1eadp: N\u1ebfu n\u00e2ng m\u1ee9c t\u1ea1 qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1eed t\u1eadp th\u00eam 3-5 rep cho m\u1ed7i set t\u1eadp. V\u00ed d\u1ee5, b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u1eadp m\u00e1y \u0111\u1ea1p \u0111\u00f9i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c t\u1ea1 40kg, 10 rep trong 3 set, th\u00ec l\u1ea7n sau b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1eed t\u0103ng th\u00eam 5 rep, t\u1eadp 15 rep trong 3 set ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 t\u0103ng th\u00eam 1 set t\u1eadp.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Gi\u1ea3m th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9: Th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c set r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f3 cho bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp. Khi b\u1ea1n t\u1eadp m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i t\u1eadp v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c set l\u00e0 1 ph\u00fat 30 gi\u00e2y, h\u00e3y gi\u1ea3m xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 1 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">2\/ Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4510\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4510\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4510 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/rau-ho-cai.png\" alt=\"ch\u1eefng c\u00e2n, ch\u1eefng c\u00e2n l\u00e0 g\u00ec, v\u00ec sao b\u1ecb ch\u1eefng c\u00e2n, kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c ch\u1eefng c\u00e2n\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/rau-ho-cai.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/rau-ho-cai-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/rau-ho-cai-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/rau-ho-cai-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/rau-ho-cai-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/rau-ho-cai-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4510\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng n\u1ebfu m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n gi\u1ea3m m\u1ee1. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong s\u1ed1 ch\u00fang ta th\u01b0\u1eddng \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n ki\u00eang t\u1eeb th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u v\u00e0 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec sai n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n th\u1ea3 l\u1ecfng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady s\u1ebd g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m ti\u00eau tan c\u00e1c n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y trong tu\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n y\u00eau th\u00edch vi\u1ec7c ra ngo\u00e0i \u0103n u\u1ed1ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n, vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf theo l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, v\u00ec v\u1eady hay theo d\u00f5i vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung calo theo tu\u1ea7n thay v\u00ec theo ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo ti\u00eau hao lu\u00f4n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo n\u1ea1p v\u00e0o.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/10-thuc-pham-giam-can-ban-nen-them-vao-thuc-don-ngay\/\">10 th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n b\u1ea1n n\u00ean th\u00eam v\u00e0o th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n ngay<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/nen-tap-gym-bao-lau-loi-ich-tap-gym-1-tieng\/\">N\u00ean t\u1eadp gym bao l\u00e2u, l\u1ee3i \u00edch t\u1eadp gym 1 ti\u1ebfng<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/cafein-anh-huong-toi-viec-tap-luyen-nhu-the-nao\/\">Cafein \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean h\u1ec7:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/@thenewgymvn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Youtube The New Gym<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/thenewgymvietnam\/\" target=\"_bla